Kwaviya chimuvimanya kuwa Mulungu hadahahulika wanhu wahasanyi, mbali munhu yoyose yoyamtegeleze Mulungu na yotenda yaja yomnogeza."
"Hachina chihulike ng'hani kuwa munhu yahulike kuwa munhu yahololile meso ya chipofu yoyalekigwe chipofu.
Habule chinhu chochose chochimtenda Mulungu yaidumwe, habule chinhu chochose chochimtenda yambule."
