"Wanangu, wanhu waja, nhogolwa ng'hani mbuli zilongigwe kwa wasaho yetu Daudi, chila munhu yahololile na kudanganika. Yamagate yake yakala hano mbaka sambi.
Munhu iyo kakala mulotezi wa Mulungu. Na viyaonile munhu iyo Mulungu viyamwing'hile kulawa mwiingalawa ya mbiki wa mtini, kakala mchanyha ya ufalume wake.
