Bahobaho mwanamke imwe yoyakalile kamulawa mgati mwa mami yake. Wanhu viwakalile woigola hana ulwivi wa Kaye ya Mulungu, waiting'hana na hanhu hatangigwe Kaye ya Mulungu hana ulwivi, kukala na chiheleto cha kusang'hana na wanhu woweng'hile mwii Kaye ya Mulungu.
