Mfalume wa longo dimwe muhala, ivo Bulahimu kasagula. Fambulo jake "Mfalume wa Ufalume," maabaho mfalume wa Salome, fambulo jake "Mfalume wa Kutosela."
"Mweye ng'hani, mgane, mkulu ng'hani, yahite kuchanyha kusongela siku izo, hebu kugendelela ugima uno, kezagaya Mwana wa Mulungu, kezahokigwa ng'hani ng'hani ng'hani kudigwa siku zose."
