Kwaviya Musa kawalongela wanhu wose malagilizo yoyose ya Malagilizo fana Musa vayalagilize. Kawalongela, "Soleni damu mwiingalawa na mazi, na kaluhulumusa makono ya langi ya zambalau, maabaho kaweng'ha chibuwa cha nyangi na kudalisa wanhu wose.
